description:
Ironically, after Leo's shoot with Phenix, Leo asked that I find a gay guy for him to work with, "I want to have sex with a guy who is really in to me."
I actually get this request often enough after I put two straight guys together. A lot of the straight guys think it will be easier if there is that "energy" there, and I have admit, it's easier when the gay guy is there and WAY in to it.
I couldn't be happier with the way Camden responded to Leo in this video. His energy emanated and bounced back threefold! These two really got into each other.
Lots of deep kissing, some great ass eating, and I love the part where Camden bobs his apple inside Leo's mouth.
So much good stuff that in fact, this video is 24 minutes, making it a rather large download of 285 megs for the largest files size. So be patient, it's worth the wait!
title: Camden & Leo - Wrapped
